#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.76"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.76:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.76:0.2"
msgid "8. Apaṇṇakavagga "
msgstr "8. Guaranteed "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.76:0.3"
msgid "76. Kusinārasutta "
msgstr "76. At Kusinārā "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an4.76:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kusinārāyaṃ viharati upavattane mallānaṃ sālavane antarena yamakasālānaṃ parinibbānasamaye. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying between a pair of <i>sal</i> trees in the <i>sal</i> forest of the Mallas at Upavattana near Kusinārā at the time of his final extinguishment. "

msgctxt "an4.76:1.2"
msgid "Tatra kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi: "
msgstr "There the Buddha addressed the mendicants, "

msgctxt "an4.76:1.3"
msgid "“bhikkhavo”ti. "
msgstr "“Mendicants!” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.76:1.4"
msgid "“Bhadante”ti te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ. "
msgstr "“Venerable sir,” they replied. "

msgctxt "an4.76:1.5"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "The Buddha said this: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an4.76:2.1"
msgid "“Siyā kho pana, bhikkhave, ekabhikkhussapi kaṅkhā vā vimati vā buddhe vā dhamme vā saṃghe vā magge vā paṭipadāya vā, pucchatha, bhikkhave, mā pacchā vippaṭisārino ahuvattha: "
msgstr "“Perhaps even a single mendicant has doubt or uncertainty regarding the Buddha, the teaching, the Saṅgha, the path, or the practice. So ask, mendicants! Don’t regret it later, thinking: "

msgctxt "an4.76:2.2"
msgid "‘sammukhībhūto no satthā ahosi, nāsakkhimha bhagavantaṃ sammukhā paṭipucchitun’”ti. "
msgstr "‘We were in the Teacher’s presence and we weren’t able to ask the Buddha a question.’” "

msgctxt "an4.76:2.3"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, te bhikkhū tuṇhī ahesuṃ. "
msgstr "When this was said, the mendicants kept silent. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an4.76:3.1"
msgid "Dutiyampi kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi: "
msgstr "For a second time the Buddha addressed the mendicants: … "

msgctxt "an4.76:3.2"
msgid "“siyā kho pana, bhikkhave, ekabhikkhussapi kaṅkhā vā vimati vā buddhe vā dhamme vā saṅghe vā magge vā paṭipadāya vā, pucchatha, bhikkhave, mā pacchā vippaṭisārino ahuvattha: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.76:3.3"
msgid "‘sammukhībhūto no satthā ahosi, nāsakkhimha bhagavantaṃ sammukhā paṭipucchitun’”ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.76:3.4"
msgid "Dutiyampi kho te bhikkhū tuṇhī ahesuṃ. "
msgstr "For a second time, the mendicants kept silent. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an4.76:4.1"
msgid "Tatiyampi kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi: "
msgstr "For a third time the Buddha addressed the mendicants: … "

msgctxt "an4.76:4.2"
msgid "“siyā kho pana, bhikkhave, ekabhikkhussapi kaṅkhā vā vimati vā buddhe vā dhamme vā saṅghe vā magge vā paṭipadāya vā, pucchatha, bhikkhave, mā pacchā vippaṭisārino ahuvattha: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.76:4.3"
msgid "‘sammukhībhūto no satthā ahosi, nāsakkhimha bhagavantaṃ sammukhā paṭipucchitun’”ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.76:4.4"
msgid "Tatiyampi kho te bhikkhū tuṇhī ahesuṃ. "
msgstr "For a third time, the mendicants kept silent. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.80, sc5
msgctxt "an4.76:5.1"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi: "
msgstr "Then the Buddha said to the mendicants: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.76:5.2"
msgid "“siyā kho pana, bhikkhave, satthugāravenapi na puccheyyātha, sahāyakopi, bhikkhave, sahāyakassa ārocetū”ti. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, perhaps you don’t ask out of respect for the Teacher. So let a friend tell a friend.” "

msgctxt "an4.76:5.3"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, te bhikkhū tuṇhī ahesuṃ. "
msgstr "When this was said, the mendicants kept silent. "

msgctxt "an4.76:5.4"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā ānando bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then Venerable Ānanda said to the Buddha: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.76:5.5"
msgid "“acchariyaṃ, bhante, abbhutaṃ, bhante. "
msgstr "“It’s incredible, sir, it’s amazing! "

msgctxt "an4.76:5.6"
msgid "Evaṃ pasanno ahaṃ, bhante. Natthi imasmiṃ bhikkhusaṅghe ekabhikkhussapi kaṅkhā vā vimati vā buddhe vā dhamme vā saṅghe vā magge vā paṭipadāya vā”ti. "
msgstr "I am quite confident that there’s not even a single mendicant in this Saṅgha who has doubt or uncertainty regarding the Buddha, the teaching, the Saṅgha, the path, or the practice.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "an4.76:6.1"
msgid "“Pasādā kho tvaṃ, ānanda, vadesi. Ñāṇameva hettha, ānanda, tathāgatassa: ‘natthi imasmiṃ bhikkhusaṅghe ekabhikkhussapi kaṅkhā vā vimati vā buddhe vā dhamme vā saṅghe vā magge vā paṭipadāya vā’. "
msgstr "“Ānanda, you speak from faith. But the Realized One knows that there’s not even a single mendicant in this Saṅgha who has doubt or uncertainty regarding the Buddha, the teaching, the Saṅgha, the path, or the practice. "

msgctxt "an4.76:6.2"
msgid "Imesañhi, ānanda, pañcannaṃ bhikkhusatānaṃ yo pacchimako bhikkhu so sotāpanno avinipātadhammo niyato sambodhiparāyaṇo”ti. "
msgstr "Even the last of these five hundred mendicants is a stream-enterer, not liable to be reborn in the underworld, bound for awakening.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.76:6.3"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

